<span class="icon-date">Posted Saturday, September 13, 2008</span> | <a href="album.asp?id=9223#postAReview" class="icon-post">Review this album</a> | <a href="https://www.progarchives.com/forum/forum_posts.asp?TID=28343" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="icon-report">Report</a> (Review #182360)
